Today’s review will be on Maybelline Color Show Lipstick. They launched some new shades recently. They are so difficult to find online as well as in ... belongs to the old Color Show collection. Let us see how it fares!

My Experience on Maybelline 115 Bling Pink Color Show Lipstick:
Packaging:
These lipsticks come in the same packaging as the normal Color Show ones. ... some shade of pink. I like how classy it looks, but I would have preferred if there was atleast a Maybelline logo. But, never mind. The packaging is nice, sturdy and travel friendly.

Color/Pigmentation:
‘Bling Pink’ is such a lovely shimmery ... barely noticeable. Once you put on the lipstick, you cannot even smell it. It has no taste, whatsoever.

Pros of Maybelline 115 Bling Pink Color Show Lipstick:

Decently priced.
Perfect shade for everyday wear.
Shimmers are not too gaudy.
Nicely pigmented.
Moisturizes the lips.
Smooth and creamy. Love the texture.
Decent staying power.

Cons of Maybelline 115 Bling Pink Color Show Lipstick:

Staying power could have been improved.

IMBB Rating:
4.8 / 5
Final Verdict:
So worth a try!

Maybelline New York Expands Shade Range of Fit Me Matte + Poreless Foundation In an Instagram post this week, Maybelline New York announced its expanding the shade range of its popular Fit Me Foundation.

Among all the high-end and drugstore foundations, Maybelline New York's Fit Me Matte + Poreless Foundation stands out as a favorite. Beauty bloggers and consumers alike go crazy ... natural-looking matte finish. But, just like with most foundations, it's hard for some people to find their perfect match. Though Maybelline has always had a decent shade range, those with yellow undertones or those whose match would be in between two shades, struggle to find their perfect hue. But all of that just changed.

This weekend, Maybelline announced via Instagram that its expanding the Fit Me Matte + Poreless Foundation by 16 (!) shades. The caption reads: ... of our retailers or in Walmart stores."

This isn't the first foundation shade range Maybelline has expanded. Last October, it added 16 colors to the Super Stay Better Skin Foundation. If you have skin thats on the more dry side, this is the face product for you.
